	<section class="py-10 my-10">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="gap-10 md:grid md:grid-cols-4">
				<div class="md:mt-5">
					<img class="w-1/2 mx-auto rounded-lg shadow-xl md:w-full md:ml-0"
						src="assets/images/dolores-carr.jpg" alt="Dr. Dolores Carr">
				</div>
				<div class="col-span-3">
					<h2 class="md:mt-3">Meet the Founder</h2>
					<p>Dr. Dolores Carr is friendly, caring, and with over 20 years of public teaching, she has an
						overwhelming
						wealth
						of
						knowledge and experience in transforming student's lives.</p>
					<x-quote cite="Dolores Carr">
						My goal is to assist students in finding their passion, then provide education options with
